ersuchen, nach der Gestaltung der neuen Bilderräume zu fragen, das Spannungsverhältnis zwischen Bildfläche und Raumkörper zu erörtern, die Beziehungen zwischen Technik, Ökonomie und (Kontroll-)Gesellschaft in den Blick zu nehmen sowie einzelne 3D-Filme in Fallstudien zu analysieren.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4a3D. 4aBild. 4aBildwissenschaft. 4aKultur. 4aMedien. 4aMediengeschichte. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aRaum. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aCulture.  aImage.  aMedia History.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.  aSpace.  aVisual Studies.1 aAndergassen, Lisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAndergassen, Lisa, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDistelmeyer, Jan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDistelmeyer, Jan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGünzel, Stephan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHanke, Christine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJockenhövel, Jesko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKap-herr, Katrin von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlippel, Heike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrautkrämer, Florian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSeeßlen, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWerdich, Nora Johanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWerdich, Nora Johanna, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part o